Hostmonitor

Ram
Total
cat /proc/meminfo | grep 'MemTotal' | awk -F ' ' '{print $2}'
Available
cat /proc/meminfo | grep 'Available' | awk -F ' ' '{print $2}'

Hdd
Total
Available
Free
df | grep '/dev/sda1 ' | awk -F ' ' '{print $2 " " $3 " " $4}'

LoadAvg
1 5 15
uptime | awk -F ' ' '{print $(NF-2) " " $(NF-1) " " $NF}'

Uptime in seconds
awk '{print $1}' /proc/uptime

Docker containers
docker ps --format '{{.Names}} {{.ID}} {{.Status}}'

